        },
        {
          "id": "b402b8d3297d_14",
          "href": null,
          "name": "72e6",
          "text": "Note: The next cohort of students in ‘Design for Sustainability’ are enrolling now! The next cohort starts in October, 2020 with the Social Dimension but you can join the current programme with the start of the Ecological Dimension in mid January 2020. This section was initially authored by José Luis Escorihuela (Ulises) and revised by Daniel Wahl in 2016.",
